cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use MolluscaGenes, please cite both the software and the associated data deposit."
title: "MolluscaGenes: a mollusc transcriptome + proteome resource with mollusc-optimized Pfam HMMs"
abstract: "Preliminary release (v0.1) of the MolluscaGenes database, containing BLAST- and DIAMOND-formatted protein and mRNA databases across ~299 mollusc species, paired with the TIAMMAt mollusc-revised Pfam HMMs (190 domains). Includes command-line wrappers for BLAST / DIAMOND / hmmsearch, species extraction, and iterative-BLAST phylogenetic placement."
type: software
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-04-27"
license: GPL-3.0-or-later
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.19825266"
repository-code: "https://github.com/invertome/molluscagenes"
